Class TokenRequest

    IBaseRequest

    public class TokenRequest
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBaseRequest
    Obtain a Secret token which needs to be used by subsequent API requests. Used internally for automatic token generation.

                    java.util.UUID posId,
                    java.util.UUID posVendorId)
        Initialise a new token request.
        Parameters:
        secret - Secret generated after sending a pairing request.
        posName - Name of the POS requesting for a token.
        posVersion - Version of the POS requesting for a token.
        posId - Generated POS ID via the POS deployment settings. Registers under the same merchant would have unique Id's
        posVendorId - ID that uniquely identifies a POS Product.
